## üí∏ COMMISSION SYSTEM

### Partner Tiers:
```
TIER 1: 0-10 order ‚Üí 30%
TIER 2: 10-25 order ‚Üí 40%
TIER 3: 50+ order ‚Üí 50%
TIER MAX: 75+ order ‚Üí 55%
Maintenance: TETAP BERTAHAN (tidak turun tier)
```

### Hierarchy Commission:
```
SPV: 10% dari partner downline + Bonus ARPU
Manager: 5% dari SPV & partner + Bonus ARPU

SPV Bonus Tiers:
- ARPU Rp 15M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 500K
- ARPU Rp 35M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 1M
- ARPU Rp 75M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 2M
- ARPU Rp 200M+ ‚Üí Bonus Rp 10M

Manager Bonus Tiers:
- ARPU Rp 45M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 1M
- ARPU Rp 105M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 2M
- ARPU Rp 225M ‚Üí Bonus Rp 3M
- ARPU Rp 600M+ ‚Üí Bonus Rp 15M
```

### Commission Rules:
- **Beli Putus:** Komisi dibayar setelah client lunas + admin approve + serah terima
- **Sewa Bulanan:** Komisi 1 bulan pertama saja, client wajib berlangganan min 3 bulan
- **Jika client stop <3 bulan:** Partner kena potong komisi

